t parameter","interleaved thinking","tool calling","MoE architecture","SWE-Bench benchmark","BrowseComp benchmark","agent workflow"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Deep reasoning mode supports \"reasoning_effort\" parameter with \"low\" and \"high\" options","API example uses model \"tencent/hy3-preview:free\" with temperature=0.9 and max_tokens=4096","\"interleaved_thinking\": True enables reasoning process display during tool usage","response.choices[0].message.reasoning_content contains the model's internal reasoning","Agent features include Tool Calling (--enable-auto-tool-choice), Interleaved Thinking, SWE-Bench Verified, and BrowseComp","Hy3 Preview achieves similar performance to Kimi-K2 with 1/4 of the parameters","Model uses MoE (Mixture of Experts) architecture","Integrated into Tencent products: Yuanbao chatbot, CodeBuddy coding assistant, WorkBuddy task helper"],"files":["/home/rg3270/blog/posts/hy3-preview-tencent.html"],"id":"obs_mra7p71p_1ddec473838c","importance":2,"narrative":"This section of the blog post documents Hy3 Preview's deep reasoning capabilities, showing how to enable reasoning_effort and access reasoning_content via the API. It also covers agent workflow optimizations including tool calling and interleaved thinking, and compares the model's efficiency against Kimi-K2 using MoE architecture.","sessionId":"ses_0c4f2c32fffeHj6r5a9OeIWnFl","subtitle":"Korean blog post documentation for Tencent Hy3 Preview model capabilities","timestamp":"2026-07-07T05:32:07.787Z","title":"Hy3 Preview blog post - reasoning and agent features","type":"file_read"},"obs_mra7p7tm_5266ab7abea8":{"concepts":["HuggingFace model card","mixture of experts LLM","vLLM inference server","SGLang serving","OpenAI-compatible API","apply_chat_template","apache-2.0 model license"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Model ID: tencent/Hy3 on Hugging Face","License: apache-2.0","Model type: Mixture of Experts (MoE), conversational text generation","Tags: Transformers, Safetensors, hy_v3, hunyuan, hy3","Community metrics: 362 likes, Tencent org 10.9k followers","Task category: Text Generation","Deployment supported: Transformers pipeline, vLLM, SGLang, Docker, llama.cpp/Ollama quantization","Key features cited: Stronger Agent Capabilities, More Reliable Product Experiences"],"files":["https://huggingface.co/tencent/Hy3"],"id":"obs_mra7p7tm_5266ab7abea8","importance":5,"narrative":"Retrieved the Hugging Face model card for Tencent's Hunyuan3 (Hy3), an open-weight mixture-of-experts text generation model. The card documents standard integration patterns via Transformers (`AutoTokenizer`, `AutoModelForCausalLM`, `apply_chat_template`) plus production serving via vLLM and SGLang with OpenAI-compatible endpoints. The apache-2.0 license makes it suitable for commercial deployment.","sessionId":"ses_0c4f2c32fffeHj6r5a9OeIWnFl","subtitle":"MoE text generation model with agent capabilities","timestamp":"2026-07-07T05:32:08.791Z","title":"Tencent Hunyuan3 (Hy3) model on Hugging Face","type":"web_fetch"},"obs_mra7p9rw_75d770056603":{"concepts":["Mixture-of-Experts (MoE)","open-source LLM release","model quantization (FP8)","context window","Apache 2.0 license"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Hy3 uses Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) architecture with 295B total parameters","21B parameters active per token plus 3.8B MTP layer parameters","Supports 256,000 token context window","Released under Apache 2.0 license on HuggingFace, ModelScope, and GitHub","FP8-quantized version available (tencent/Hy3-FP8)","Blind evaluation by 270 experts: scored 2.67/4 vs GLM-5.1 at 2.51","Hallucination rate reduced from 12.5% to 5.4%","OpenRouter and Cline support planned"],"files":["https://huggingface.co/tencent/Hy3","https://huggingface.co/tencent/Hy3-FP8","https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/Hy3","https://modelscope.cn/models/Tencent-Hunyuan/Hy3","https://the-decoder.com/tencent-releases-hy3-open-source-model-that-allegedly-matches-models-up-to-five-times-its-active-size/"],"id":"obs_mra7p9rw_75d770056603","importance":5,"narrative":"Tencent released Hy3, an open-source MoE model claiming to match performance of models 2-5x its size. The model demonstrates efficient inference with only 21B active parameters out of 295B total, while achieving competitive benchmark scores and lower hallucination rates than comparable models.","sessionId":"ses_0c4f2c32fffeHj6r5a9OeIWnFl","subtitle":"295B parameter model with 21B active parameters claims performance competitive with models 2-5x its size","timestamp":"2026-07-07T05:32:11.322Z","title":"Tencent releases Hy3 open-source MoE model","type":"web_fetch"},"obs_mra7pk2g_6173ac622661":{"concepts":["blog post management","duplicate content detection","HTML file enumeration","WSL command execution"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Found 2 Tencent-related HTML files: hy3-preview-tencent.html and tencent-workbuddy-ai-workplace-agent.html","No other hunyuan or hy3 files detected in the posts directory","Recent 15 files include tencent-workbuddy-ai-workplace-agent.html","Command executed via WSL: wsl.exe python3 -c \"...\""],"files":["/home/rg3270/blog/posts/hy3-preview-tencent.html","/home/rg3270/blog/posts/tencent-workbuddy-ai-workplace-agent.html"],"id":"obs_mra7pk2g_6173ac622661","importance":3,"narrative":"Ran a Python script via WSL to scan the blog posts directory for duplicate Tencent-related HTML files. The search identified exactly two Tencent-associated posts: a Hunyuan3 preview and the Workbuddy AI agent article. No duplicates were detected, and the Workbuddy post appears among the most recent blog entries.","sessionId":"ses_0c4f2c32fffeHj6r5a9OeIWnFl","subtitle":"Searched blog/posts directory for Tencent-related HTML files and reviewed recent additions","timestamp":"2026-07-07T05:32:24.662Z","title":"Check for duplicate Tencent blog posts","type":"command_run"},"obs_mra7rtap_5bf478556ede":{"concepts":["HTML blog templates","CSS responsive design","code syntax highlighting","collapsible code blocks"],"confidence":1,"facts"