ome extension via WebSocket","Key design principles: in-page execution, text-based DOM, bring-your-own LLM (OpenAI-compatible), progressive enhancement","Optional layers include UI panel, Chrome extension, and MCP server built on top of the headless core agent","Source files referenced: README.md, packages/core/src/PageAgentCore.ts, AGENTS.md","Supports integration with Qwen, OpenAI, DeepSeek, and other OpenAI-compatible LLM providers"],"files":["README.md","packages/core/src/PageAgentCore.ts","AGENTS.md"],"id":"obs_mraeducw_fb2a6d8c1c1f","importance":6,"narrative":"Retrieved an overview of Alibaba's Page Agent project, an in-browser AI agent that controls web interfaces through natural language via text-based DOM manipulation. The architecture uses a ReAct loop for reasoning and action execution, designed as a layered TypeScript monorepo with a headless core that can be embedded anywhere. This matters as a reference for building client-side AI agents without infrastructure overhead.","sessionId":"ses_0c4f2c32fffeHj6r5a9OeIWnFl","subtitle":"Alibaba's open-source in-page AI GUI agent architecture","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:39:15.435Z","title":"Page Agent Repository Overview","type":"web_fetch"},"obs_mraedut7_abe197fd4e60":{"concepts":["hook system","workflow step"],"confidence":0.9,"facts":["Hook type: step_finish","Timestamp: 2026-07-07T08:39:16.023Z"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mraedut7_abe197fd4e60","importance":1,"narrative":"A step completion hook was triggered at the specified timestamp, indicating that a workflow step has finished execution. No substantive content or technical artifacts were provided in this observation.","sessionId":"ses_0c4f2c32fffeHj6r5a9OeIWnFl","subtitle":"Process step completion signal received","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:39:16.023Z","title":"Step finish hook triggered","type":"notification"},"obs_mraee30n_329c45807027":{"concepts":["web scraping","client-side rendering","documentation fetching","GUI agents","browser extensions"],"confidence"